{"tid":2458363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[新移民刷首抽失敗]兩女子疑吃河豚後中毒　入院治療情況穩定","createTime":"2021-03-23T11:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T11:16:26.000Z","uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c4cd0645dac2f001422e99552dc4578e25bb1139","tid":2458363,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:07:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582150-20210323.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582150-20210323.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97WINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=21da71ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582150-20210323.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=dcf50cf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582150-20210323.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n兩名女子懷疑進食河豚後中毒，前往屯門醫院急症室求醫，入院接受治療，現時情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心表示，兩名女子分別18及45歲，星期日一同在家中進食朋友在本港捕獲並經烹煮的河豚魚子後，即時至約11小時後出現舌頭和嘴唇麻痺、暈眩及四肢無力和麻痺。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心指出，進食河豚是河豚毒素引致食物中毒的主要原因。河豚毒素是一種毒性強烈的水溶性神經毒素，可影響中樞神經系統，嚴重可能會致命，現時沒有已知的解毒劑或抗毒素可分解河豚毒素，提醒市民切勿進食河豚。"},{"pid":"065dd593c98d07d58a2f534799cec05f70b7537f","tid":2458363,"uid":374134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:09:08.000Z","msg":"咁便宜佢哋 送佢哋一程呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4a788db54653e507c6f01da23ccd961b1dcdb2","tid":2458363,"uid":7323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">屌你老母，咁都唔死</span>"},{"pid":"32d15be80cd94d12e1c96c695d113b72a2a3c05b","tid":2458363,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:12:22.000Z","msg":"在本港捕獲並經烹煮的河豚魚子?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4064968f20aa91e5f6f6f1b5e45a73ced14a0b6","tid":2458363,"uid":38143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:13:17.000Z","msg":"痴撚線魚春最毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8a4c39df9944998903e4bfbaa55907c2f13416","tid":2458363,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:14:18.000Z","msg":"家中進食朋友在本港捕獲並經烹煮的河豚魚子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7b72a55d0c1ea068f6c6f078ae282a8c5f6624","tid":2458363,"uid":156096,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c4cd0645dac2f001422e99552dc4578e25bb1139","tid":2458363,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:07:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582150-20210323.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582150-20210323.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97WINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=21da71ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582150-20210323.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=dcf50cf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582150-20210323.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n兩名女子懷疑進食河豚後中毒，前往屯門醫院急症室求醫，入院接受治療，現時情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心表示，兩名女子分別18及45歲，星期日一同在家中進食朋友在本港捕獲並經烹煮的河豚魚子後，即時至約11小時後出現舌頭和嘴唇麻痺、暈眩及四肢無力和麻痺。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心指出，進食河豚是河豚毒素引致食物中毒的主要原因。河豚毒素是一種毒性強烈的水溶性神經毒素，可影響中樞神經系統，嚴重可能會致命，現時沒有已知的解毒劑或抗毒素可分解河豚毒素，提醒市民切勿進食河豚。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"兩名女子懷疑進食河豚後中毒，前往屯門醫院急症室求醫，入院接受治療，現時情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心表示，兩名女子分別18及45歲，星期日一同在家中進食朋友在本港捕獲並經烹煮<span class=\"red\">的河豚魚子</span>後，即時至約11小時後出現舌頭和嘴唇麻痺、暈眩及四肢無力和麻痺。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心指出，進食河豚是河豚毒素引致食物中毒的主要原因。河豚毒素是一種毒性強烈的水溶性神經毒素，可影響中樞神經系統，嚴重可能會致命，現時沒有已知的解毒劑或抗毒素可分解河豚毒素，提醒市民切勿進食河豚。<br />\n<br />\n仲要唔毒果部分唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}